The paper deals with a graph optimization problem involving pricing and payment, which suggests that it could belong to the sub-categories of algorithms and data structures (cs.DS), game theory (cs.GT), computational complexity (cs.CC), information theory (cs.IT), or machine learning (cs.LG). However, the focus on graph optimization and pricing makes cs.DS and cs.GT the most likely categories, followed by cs.CC, cs.IT, and cs.LG.
